snippet.title: OutRun playthrough (Game Boy Advance) (1CC)
snippet.description: This video shows the route to the C ending. This version of the game was included on SEGA Arcade Gallery. It's much easier than any of the other ports I've played, as you can crash several times and still finish the course with plenty of time to spare. The options menu doesn't have options for difficulty, so it looks like this version is permanently set on easy.
